# Fade

## Import

```jsx live=false
import { Fade } from '@totejs/uikit';
```

## Usage

### Fade transition

```jsx
function FadeEx() {
  const { isOpen, onToggle } = useDisclosure();

  return (
    <>
      <Button onClick={onToggle}>Click Me</Button>
      <Fade in={isOpen}>
        <Box
          p={40}
          color="white"
          mt="12"
          bg="scene.success.normal"
          borderRadius={8}
        >
          Some Text
        </Box>
      </Fade>
    </>
  );
}
```

